# 🔐 Password Generator & Strength Checker - Python GUI

A simple yet powerful **Password Generator** with real-time **Strength Checker**, built using **Python Tkinter**. This tool helps you generate secure passwords and check their strength instantly.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Generate strong passwords with:
  - Lowercase letters
  - Uppercase letters
  - Numbers
  - Special characters

- ✅ Strength meter with progress bar
- ✅ Copy password to clipboard
- ✅ User-friendly Tkinter GUI

